      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for this awesome ride. It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is still in really solid shape for its next owner! It runs great, looks sharp, and is just perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend road trips. I've taken good care of it, and it's totally ready to hit the road today. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
