    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This A80 chassis features the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six, retaining its factory sequential twin-turbochargers and side-mount intercooler. Power is delivered through the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission to a Torsen limited-slip differential. The vehicle maintains its original suspension geometry with independent double-wishbone architecture and four-piston front calipers. Recent preventative maintenance includes a timing belt service and fresh valve cover gaskets. This is a mechanically sound, high-performance platform offering linear boost response and exceptional structural rigidity, ideal for the enthusiast who values engineering integrity.",
      "price": 36500.0,
